# direnv template: conda environment
#
# Usage: copy into your project root as `.envrc`, then run `direnv allow`.
#
# Requires the `layout_anaconda` helper from direnv/direnvrc in this repo,
# symlinked to ~/.config/direnv/direnvrc.
#
# Replace "myenv" with the conda environment name for this project — it
# must already exist (create it first with `conda create -n myenv ...`).

layout anaconda myenv
